Create an application with two buttons named as Toast Button and Increment Button
and also TextView with value displayed as Zero initially. when the user clicks on Toast
Button, Toast message to be displayed. when user clicks on Increment Button, it
displays the current count after Count is tapped. Each tap increases the count by one.
